=companyResearch
assignments.value: ={{(() => {   try {     const debug = $json;     const primary = debug.primaryCompany?.articles || [];     return primary.length ? primary.map(a => `- ${a.title}`).join('\n') : null;   } catch (e) {     return null;   } })()}}

assignments.name: =industryReserach
assignments.value: ={{(() => {   try {     const debug = $json;     const industry = debug.industryNews || [];     return industry.length ? industry.map(a => `- ${a.title}`).join('\n') : null;   } catch (e) {     return null;   } })()}}

assignments.name: =socialMedia
assignments.value: ={{(() => {   try {     const debug = $json;     const social = debug.data?.find(d => d.type === 'social_media_analysis');     const mentions = social?.socialMentions || [];     return mentions.map(m => `- ${m.title} (${m.sentiment})`).join('\n') || null;   } catch (e) {     return null;   } })()}}
